    "LLMs and VLMs have strong logical reasoning and visual perception capabilities, which enable robots to complete task planning with a full understanding of the task scenario and human instructions, and Fig. 5 Vision and language task planning adapted with permission from Hu et al.",
    "promote effective communication and collaboration between humans and robots.",
    "Table 3 lists the representative results of the recent application of VLMs or LLMs to robot task planning.",
    "Task understanding and decomposition is the first step in task planning, which involves extracting task objectives from natural language descriptions and decomposing complex tasks into a series of manageable subtasks.",
    "VLMs play a crucial role in this process as they can extract rich semantic information from text and images."
